{
  "section_id": "11-why-rl-for-biology-can-be-chal",
  "title": "Why RL for Biology Can be Challenging",
  "title_translation": "为什么生物学领域的强化学习充满挑战",
  "paragraphs": [
    {
      "id": "p000",
      "index": 0,
      "source": "Scientific experiments can vary wildly in time required for completion. In biology, plenty of experiments take days to complete. These longer timelines require long rollouts, meaning rewards will be sparse. Sparse rewards provide less signal for the model to learn from.",
